%20presidential%20candidates%20for%20the%202024%20election%20very%20(28%25)%20or%20fairly%20(40%25)%20closely.%20But%20what%20exactly%20were%20they%20getting%20or%20hoping%20to%20get%3F%20The%20survey%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmericans%20most%20often%20see%20news%20about%20actions%20on%20the%20presidential%20campaign%20trail%2C%20though%20they%20are%20most%20interested%20in%20their%20stances%20on%20issues%E2%80%9D.%20A%20fair%20ask.%20Obviously%20unmet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECircus%20Of%20The%20Absurd%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20American%20voter%20has%20received%20so%20far%20is%20a%20concept%20of%20a%20plan%20from%20Trump%20and%20a%20promised%20continuum%20of%20Biden's%20%E2%80%98problematic'%20policies%20from%20Harris.%20Many%20Americans%20are%20sitting%20this%20election%20out%2C%20and%20who%20can%20blame%20them%3F%20A%20campaign%20trail%20inundated%20with%20descriptions%20of%20a%20golfer's%20penis%20or%20how%20immigrants%20are%20eating%20other%20people's%20animals%2C%20insinuations%20about%20a%20potential%20election%20steal%20on%20one%20side%20and%20an%20undressed%20stream-of-consciousness%20word%20salad%20on%20the%20other%2C%20has%20done%20little%20to%20convince%20the%20average%20American%20voter%20about%20the%20nobility%20and%20grandiosity%20of%20the%20White%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20have%20demonstrated%20an%20utter%20inability%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20past.%20While%20Trump%20got%20too%20bored%20of%20a%20decent%2C%20non-dramatic%20campaign%20just%20a%20few%20months%20into%202024%20and%20unleashed%20his%202020%20MAGA-man%20energy%2C%20Harris%20stubbornly%20refused%20to%20bring%20any%20course%20correction%20in%20her%20agenda%20on%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20despite%20her%20fellow%20Democrats'%20public%20castigation.%20This%20election%20has%20been%20the%20most%20extensive%20testimony%20of%20what%20a%20lot%20of%20analysts%20within%20the%20US%2C%20as%20well%20as%20outside%2C%20have%20observed%20but%20have%20largely%20refrained%20from%20verbalising%3A%20both%20the%20Democrats%20and%20the%20Republicans%20fashion%20their%20electoral%20campaigns%20around%20the%20faults%20of%20the%20other%20side%20while%20doing%20absolutely%20nothing%20about%20their%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKamala%2C%20The%20Saner%20One%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20not%20ridiculous%20that%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20posited%20her%20only%20as%20the%20saner%20alternative%20to%20Trump%3F%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20Democrat%20incumbency%20became%20a%20burden%20and%20not%20a%20bolster%20for%20Harris%20should%20alert%20us%20that%20the%20new%20president's%20arrival%20in%20the%20White%20House%20will%20probably%20be%20an%20extension%20of%20all%20the%20gaffes%20this%20campaign%20saw.%20And%20what%20about%20the%20process%20of%20candidate%20selection%20for%20both%20parties%3F%20Declaring%20Trump%20as%20their%20candidate%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20the%20Republican%20Party%20demonstrated%20an%20utter%20lack%20of%20imagination%20at%20a%20time%20when%20President%20Biden's%20popularity%20was%20ebbing%20steadily.%20The%20Democrats%20changed%20their%20candidate%20from%20Biden%20to%20Harris%20with%20almost%20nil%20deliberations%20in%20their%20convention.%20The%20working-class%20voters%2C%20cold%20about%20Biden%2C%20have%20stayed%20cold%20towards%20her%20as%20well%20throughout%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20US%20presidential%20elections%20are%20not%20about%20the%20American%20voters%20alone.%20What%20happens%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20reverberates%20throughout%20the%20world.%20When%20Barack%20Obama%20won%20his%20first%20term%2C%20the%20symbolism%20of%20this%20victory%20was%20evident%20from%20young%20and%20old%20Indians%20celebrating%20at%20the%20India%20Gate%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Presidents%20come%20and%20go%2C%20but%20their%20road%20to%20the%20Capitol%20paves%20ways%20across%20the%20world%20for%20ideologies%2C%20ideas%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20ramifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENobody%20Knows%20Anything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20formulating%20trade%20controls%20to%20funding%20wars%2C%20what%20the%20POTUS%20decides%20goes%20a%20long%20way%20for%20the%20US%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20Both%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20turned%20serious%20policy%20issues%20into%20farce%20during%20the%20campaign%20by%20sharpening%20the%20focus%20only%20on%20each%20other's%20personalities.%20We%20still%20do%20not%20know%20what%20Trump's%20plan%20is%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20or%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%20Or%20China.%20Or%20Sudan%20or%20Bangladesh%2C%20for%20that%20matter.%20We%20only%20know%20that%20Harris%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccommitted%20to%20peace%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20her%20party's%20ongoing%20actions%20have%20suggested%20otherwise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%2C%20it%20is%20an%20exercise%20in%20futility%20to%20assess%20what%20a%20Trump%20or%20a%20Harris%20win%20might%20mean%20for%20India%20or%20the%20larger%20Global%20South.%20There%20are%20no%20guiding%20principles%20to%20launch%20any%20such%20enquiry.%20Any%20scenario%20study%20will%20yield%20only%20fallacious%20conclusions%20because%2C%20simply%2C%20neither%20Trump%20nor%20Harris%20has%20stuck%20to%20either%20the%20party%20line%20or%20even%20their%20own%20stated%20beliefs.%20Trump's%20transactionalism%20and%20Harris's%20hubris%20are%20enough%20to%20defy%20any%20projections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20presidential%20election%20was%20once%20a%20lesson%20in%20how%20democracy%20asserts%20itself.%20In%202024%2C%20it%20has%20become%20something%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20glorified%20version%20of%20Hulk%20Hogan%20wrestling%20with%20his%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A173