%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20Fluoride%20And%20Why%20Trump%20Would%20Remove%20It%20From%20Drinking%20Water%20If%20He%20Wins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20voting%20for%20the%20US%20Presidential%20polls%2C%20former%20independent%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20re-elected%2C%20would%20aim%20to%20remove%20fluoride%20from%20public%20drinking%20water%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20January%2020%2C%20the%20Trump%20White%20House%20will%20advise%20all%20U.S.%20water%20systems%20to%20remove%20fluoride%20from%20public%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20wrote%20on%20X.%20He%20claimed%20fluoride%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bindustrial%20waste%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20various%20health%20risks%2C%20such%20as%20bone%20fractures%2C%20neurodevelopmental%20disorders%2C%20and%20IQ%20loss%2C%20adding%20that%20Trump%20and%20former%20First%20Lady%20Melania%20Trump%20seek%20to%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Healthy%20Again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2020%2C%20the%20Trump%20White%20House%20will%20advise%20all%20U.S%E2%80%8B.%20water%20systems%20to%20remove%20fluoride%20from%20public%20water.%20Fluoride%20is%20an%20industrial%20waste%20associated%20with%20arthritis%2C%20bone%20fractures%2C%20bone%20cancer%2C%20IQ%20loss%2C%20neurodevelopmental%20disorders%2C%20and%20thyroid%20disease.%20President%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr%20(%40RobertKennedyJr)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRobertKennedyJr%2Fstatus%2F1852812012478398923%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20statements%20came%20after%20his%20continued%20opposition%20to%20fluoridation%2C%20a%20stance%20often%20criticised%20by%20the%20broader%20medical%20community.%20Trump%2C%20who%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-says-vaccine-skeptic-rfk-jr-will-have-big-role-in-health-care-if-he-wins-6927221%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20make%20Kennedy%20a%20key%20figure%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20healthcare%20policy%20if%20re-elected%2C%20has%20been%20open%20to%20reviewing%20such%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024-election%2Ftrump-banning-vaccines-president-rfk-fluoride-rcna178570%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20talked%20to%20him%20about%20it%20yet%2C%20but%20it%20sounds%20OK%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%20before%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20also%20willing%20to%20consult%20with%20other%20experts%2C%20calling%20Kennedy%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20talented%20guy%20with%20strong%20views.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Fluoride%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFluoride%2C%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20mineral%2C%20is%20commonly%20added%20to%20public%20drinking%20water%20to%20prevent%20tooth%20decay%2C%20a%20practice%20endorsed%20by%20numerous%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFluoride%20is%20a%20natural%20substance%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Oliver%20Jones%20of%20RMIT%20University%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Fnov%2F04%2Ffluoride-explainer-what-is-us-election-donald-trump-robert-f-kennedy-jr%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ethe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20an%20industrial%20waste%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDental%20experts%20have%20long%20touted%20fluoride's%20benefits%2C%20explaining%20that%20it%20strengthens%20tooth%20enamel%20and%20helps%20protect%20against%20cavities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudies%20linking%20fluoride%20to%20serious%20health%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20cancer%20or%20neurological%20problems%2C%20remain%20inconclusive.%20%26quot%3BContrary%20to%20Kennedy's%20claims%2C%20studies%20have%20found%20no%20evidence%20linking%20fluoride%20in%20regular%20drinking%20water%20to%20conditions%20such%20as%20osteoporosis%2C%20bone%20fractures%2C%20or%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Loc%20Do%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20and%20the%20US%20Centres%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20(CDC)%20endorse%20fluoride's%20safety.%20They%20have%20set%20a%20recommended%20limit%20of%201.5%20mg%20per%20litre%20for%20drinking%20water.%20Fluoridation%20was%20named%20one%20of%20the%20top%2010%20public%20health%20achievements%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20by%20the%20CDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Potential%20Health%20Agenda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20has%20previously%20signalled%20a%20willingness%20to%20entertain%20Kennedy's%20views%2C%20including%20on%20other%20contentious%20health%20topics%20such%20as%20vaccine%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20banning%20certain%20vaccines%2C%20Trump%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20talk%20to%20(Kennedy)%20and%20talk%20to%20other%20people%2C%20and%20I'll%20make%20a%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20counting%20has%20started%20for%20the%20US%20elections%20with%20several%20media%20networks%20currently%20projecting%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20winning%2010%20states%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20winning%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20electoral%20college%20numbers%2C%20which%20will%20determine%20the%20winner%20in%20this%20election%2C%20the%20former%20President%20is%20ahead%20with%20137%20votes%20and%20Harris%20trails%20with%2099.%20Each%20candidate%20is%20aiming%20for%20the%20magic%20figur