e%20mistake%2C%20which%20can%20take%20several%20days%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-results-trump-harris-presidential-election-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprolong%20the%20vote-counting%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsl.org%2Felections-and-campaigns%2Ftable-15-states-with-signature-cure-processes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Conference%20of%20State%20Legislatures.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBallots%20lacking%20verifiable%20signatures%20are%20not%20counted%20in%20states%20without%20a%20curing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20Election%20Day%2C%20more%20than%2011%2C300%20mail-in%20ballots%20needed%20signatures%20cured%20in%20Clark%20County%2C%20and%20more%20than%201%2C800%20needed%20fixing%20in%20Washoe%20County%2C%20the%20Nevada%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nvsos.gov%2Fsos%2Fhome%2Fshowpublisheddocument%2F15255%2F638663412093330000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecretary%20of%20state's%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20As%20the%20state%20continues%20to%20process%20mail%20ballots%20this%20week%2C%20those%20figures%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20already%20higher%20than%20in%202020%20and%202022%20%E2%80%94%20are%20expected%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20to%20look%20at%20the%20data%2C%20and%20you%20start%20to%20realize%20how%20high%20it%20is%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20nervous%20because%2C%20again%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-donald-trump-swing-states-sun-belt-polls-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20races%20are%20so%20close%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20margins%20are%20so%20slim%2C%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20tonight%20and%20know%20that%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20ballots%20to%20be%20cured%2C%26quot%3B%20Aguilar%20told%20the%20Times%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%2