l%20Security%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fundamental%20problem%20here%20is%20that%20a%20signature%20is%20not%20a%20unique%20identifier%2C%26quot%3B%20Cleaver%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20secondary%20problem%20is%20that%20schools%20don't%20teach%20cursive%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202010%2C%20many%20states%20have%20dropped%20the%20skill%20from%20their%20curricula%20as%20part%20of%20the%20widespread%20shift%20to%20the%20Common%20Core%20State%20Standards%20for%20English%2C%20which%20didn't%20explicitly%20include%20cursive%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20people%20now%20in%20their%20late%20teens%20and%20early%2020s%20had%20little%20to%20no%20cursive%20instruction%20and%20few%20opportunities%20to%20practice%20developing%20their%20unique%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20all%20these%20people%20who%20don't%20have%20signatures%20and%20not%20experience%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Cleaver%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20become%20an%20increasing%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20several%20states%2C%20including%20California%20and%20Louisiana%2C%20have%20passed%20legislation%20to%20reintroduce%20the%20skill%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-voters-struggle-signatures-cast-mail-ballot-problems-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730857439000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672aba1088cea3ba1c1e964d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-voters-struggle-signatures-cast-mail-ballot-problems-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Young%20voters%20in%20Nevada%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20didn't%20grow%20up%20learning%20cursive%20in%20school%2C%20are%20having%20difficulty%20voting%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20state%20said%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnod