%2C%20the%20woman%20offered%20to%20work%20for%20free%20for%20a%20month.%20Not%20just%20this%2C%20she%20also%20said%20her%20employer%20could%20fire%20her%20without%20notice%20or%20compensation%20if%20unhappy%20with%20her%20work.%20She%20even%20promised%20to%20work%20overtime%20and%20without%20weekly%20offs%2C%20just%20so%20she%20could%20stay%20on%20in%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHire%20me%20for%20free%20for%20one%20month.%20If%20I%20don't%20deliver%2C%20fire%20me%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%20My%20Graduate%20Visa%20EXPIRES%20in%203%20months%2C%20repost%20this%20to%20help%20me%20stay%20in%20the%20UK%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20pleaded%20on%20LinkedIn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20market%20feels%20like%20there's%20no%20value%20for%20me%2C%20my%20degree%2C%20or%20my%20capabilities...%20I%20have%20applied%20to%20300%2B%20jobs%20and%20got%20a%20handful%20of%20useful%20feedback.%20This%20LinkedIn%20post%20is%20my%20FINAL%20chance%20to%20secure%20a%20long-term%20future%20in%20the%20UK%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7248082260254429184%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221467%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20student%20wrote%20that%20she%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bvisa-sponsored%20Designer%20Engineer%20role%26quot%3B%20and%20highlighted%20her%20qualifications%20in%20her%20post.%20She%20boldly%20offered%20to%20work%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20to%20demonstrate%20her%20value.%20On%20top%20of%20this%2C%20she%20also%20said%20that%20her%20employers%20could%20fire%20her%20without%20notice%20or%20compensation%20if%20unhappy%20with%20her%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20UK%20employer%20hiring%20for%20Design%20Engineer%20roles%2C%20you%20won't%20regret%20hiring%20me.%20I'll%20work%2012%20hours%20per%20day%20and%207%20days%20a%20week%20to%20prove%20my%20worth.%20If%20you're%20an%20international%20student%20reading%20this%2C%20I%20would%20be%20eternally%20grateful%20if%20you%20could%20repost%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20post%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20a%20month%20back%2C%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FIndianWorkplace%2Fcomments%2F1g75iw9%2Fwith_attitude_and_approach_like_thisforget_about%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dweb3x%26utm_name%3Dweb3xcss%26utm_term%3D1%26utm_content%3Dshare_button%5C%22%3EReddit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20garnered%20mixed%20reactions%20from%20social%20media.%20While%20some%20criticised%20the%20woman%20for%20going%20to%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20lengths%20to%20avoid%20returning%20to%20work%2C%20others%20slammed%20her%20for%20creating%20unrealistic%20expectations%20for%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResponsibly%20ruining%20the%20image%20of%20Indians%20abroad%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20severely%20hurting%20the%20chances%20of%20those%20genuine%20candidates%20who%20can%20make%20it%20big%20abroad.%20This%20is%20usually%20the%20case%20with%20most%20rich%2Fspoiled%20folks%20who%20don't%20think%20twice%20before%20pursuing%20Master's%20abroad%2C%20and%20when%20reality%20hits%20them%20in%20the%20face%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20graduate%20program%2C%20it's%20game%20over.%20Sad%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20for%20free%20thinking%20companies%20would%20not%20take%20advantage%20of%20it%20and%20creating%20this%20entire%20hell%20hole%20all%20together%20is%20crazy%20%2C%20in%20this%20job%20market%3F%20Why%20the%20f**k%20are%20these%20grads%20doing%20it%3F%20What%20in%20name%20of%20wanting%20to%20be%20slave%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstro