poll%20found%20that%20only%207%25%20of%20voters%20were%20%26quot%3Benthusiastic%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20nation's%20direction.%20More%20voters%2C%2029%25%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Bangry%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20country's%20direction%2C%20the%20most%20pessimistic%20option%20available.%20Overall%2C%20only%2026%25%20of%20voters%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bsatisfied%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20nation's%20direction.%20In%20contrast%2C%2072%25%20of%20voters%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bdissatisfied.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20voters%20made%20up%20their%20minds%20long%20before%20November%2C%20according%20to%20CNN's%20exit%20poll%2C%20which%20found%20that%20eight%20in%2010%20voters%20made%20their%20decision%20about%20the%20presidential%20election%20before%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20suggests%20Trump%20could%20survive%20the%20damage%20brought%20on%20by%20his%20controversial%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-madison-square-garden-rally-overshadow-economy-puerto-rico-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20could%20also%20mean%20that%20Harris'%20strong%20debate%20performance%20on%20September%2010%20may%20have%20come%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215729b0a-41c1-4bdf-969a-d43a46391721%5C%22%3EWhen%20we'll%20know%20the%20results%20in%20each%20state%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20states%2C%20we%20may%20know%20the%20results%20pretty%20quickly.%20In%20others%2C%20counting%20may%20take%20days.%20Poll%20closing%20times%20listed%20below%20are%20in%20Eastern%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Polls%20have%20now%20closed%20in%20most%20of%20Georgia%2C%20though%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-poll-bomb-threats-russia-election-harris-trump-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandful%20of%20polling%20places%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20remaining%20open%20late%20due%20to%20bomb%20threats.%20A%20winner%20could%20be%20declared%20in%20the%20Peach%20State%20by%20late%20Tuesday%20night.%20Though%20the%20state%20took%20days%20to%20process%20mail-in%20ballots%20in%202020%2C%20a%20new%20law%20allowed%20election%20officials%20to%20begin%20tabulating%20those%20votes%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20likely%20speeding%20up%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Polls%20have%20now%20closed%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20counted%20votes%20quickly.%20A%20winner%20could%20be%20declared%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Polls%20close%20in%20Michigan%20and%20Pennsylvania.%20Michigan%20is%20expected%20to%20count%20ballots%20relatively%20quickly%20and%20could%20announce%20a%20result%20Tuesday%20night%20or%20early%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Pennsylvania%20count%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20days.%20That's%20because%20the%20election%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20so%20close%20in%20the%20Keystone%20State%20and%20because%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20electorate%20votes%20by%20mail%2C%20and%20officials%20can't%20begin%20to%20count%20those%20votes%20until%20polls%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20most%20news%20outlets%20didn't%20call%20Pennsylvania%20until%20Saturday%20%E2%80%94%20at%20which%20point%20Joe%20Biden%20became%20president-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9%20p.m.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Polls%20close%20in%20Wisconsin%20and%20Arizona.%20We%20may%20not%20know%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F09%2F22%2Fpolitics%2Fvote-counting-delays-election-states%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20in%20Wisconsin%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20state%20election%20official%20told%20CNN%20in%20September%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20count%20absentee%20ballots%20in%20the%20heavily%20Democratic%20city%20of%20Milwau