%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FDay-4-Noble-1730298952.jpg%3Fresize%3D600%252C450%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FDay-4-Noble-1730298952.jpg%3Fresize%3D400%252C300%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FDay-4-Noble-1730298952.jpg%3Fresize%3D200%252C150%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FDay-4-Noble-1730298952.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C113%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMDA%20has%20faithfully%20served%20children%20with%20dyslexia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20personal%20motivation%20for%20establishing%20MDA%20was%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20professionals%20who%20could%20help%20my%20son.%20Initially%2C%20the%20MDA%20encountered%20a%20lot%20of%20problems.%20Firstly%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20clarity%20about%20what%20dyslexia%20is.%20Many%20parents%20were%20in%20denial%20that%20their%20children%20could%20have%20dyslexia.%20There%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20thought%20that%20we%20were%20supporting%20%E2%80%98dumb%E2%80%99%20children.%20But%20we%20would%20overcome%20these%20challenges%20over%20time%20through%20our%20relentless%20awareness%20programmes%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20parents%2C%20schools%20and%20the%20general%20public%20through%20the%20media%2C%20while%20also%20actively%20providing%20special%20assistance%20to%20dyslexic%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20MDA%20do%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20MDA%20started%20with%20training%20teachers%20to%20help%20children%20with%20dyslexia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20D%20Chandrasekhar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20opened%20a%20remediation%20centre%2C%20both%20part-time%20and%20full-time%2C%20for%20children%20and%20also%20got%20a%20few%20of%20our%20special%20educators%20trained%20to%20carry%20out%20assessments.%20We%20adopted%20many%20techniques%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F285225%2Fwhen-an-indian-mp-challenged-racism-in-america-forced-us-govt-to-apologise%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20modify%20this%20programme%20to%20suit%20Indian%20children.%20Accordingly%2C%20our%20teachers%20employed%20a%20lot%20of%20innovation%20in%20converting%20these%20practices%20to%20suit%20our%20conditions.%20We%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20developments%20in%20remediating%20through%20multiple%20sensory%20techniques%20using%20verbal%2C%20auditory%2C%20kinesthetic%2C%20and%20tactile%20techniques.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20MDA%20runs%20the%20full-time%20remediation%20centre%20for%20severely%20affected%20dyslexic%20children.%20They%20support%2030%20children%20at%20their%20centre%20besides%20providing%20part-time%20remediation%20to%2050%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20the%20teachers%20on%20how%20to%20identify%20these%20children%20using%20a%20checklist.%20We%20also%20train%20the%20teachers%20how%20to%20use%20multi-sensory%20techniques%20and%20remediate%20the%20children%20from%20their%20problems%20in%20reading%2C%20writing%2C%20spelling%2C%20maths%2C%20and%20executive%20functions.%20We%20train%20the%20trainee%20teachers%20to%20show%20a%20lot%20of%20empathy%20and%20understanding%20to%20the%20children%20with%20dyslexia%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20teachers%2C%20MDA%20runs%20an%20e-shikshanam%20programme%20that%20is%20essentially%20a%20free%20even-week%20online%20course%20that%20helps%20primary%20school%20teachers%20support%20children%20with%20mild%20to%20moderate%20dyslexia.%20They%20also%20run%20a%20six-week%20Intensive%20Teacher%20Training%20Programme%20that%20helps%20teachers%20identify%20and%20support%20children%20with%20different%20levels%20of%20dyslexia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20remediation%20sessions%20for%20children%20are%20done%20through%20the%20ALRC.%20This%20includes%20an%C2%A0%20Individual%20Education%20Program%20(IEP)%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20MDA%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20drawn%20out%20for%20the%20child%20based%20on%20his%2Fher%20strengths%20and%20needs.%E2%80%9D%20The%20IEP%20consists%20of%20%E2%80%9Cskill%20building%2C%20need-based%20and%20activity%20oriented%20learning%E2%80%9D.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20ALRC%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98holistic%20development%20of%20the%20child%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20nurture%20their%20talents%20and%20interests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20co-curricular%20activities%20like%20yoga%2C%20music%2C%20dramatics%2C%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20and%20games%2C%20besides%20something%20called%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHydra%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CHydra%20is%20one%20of%20the%20arms%20of%20MDA%20focussed%20on%20nurturing%20the%20natural%20potential%20of%20children.%20The%20team%20at%20Hydra%20consists%20of%20trained%20teachers%20and%20mental%20health%20professionals%20and%20works%20in%20technical%20partnership%20with%20Vidya%20Sagar%20%5Ba%20Chennai-based%20non-profit%20empowering%20people%20with%20disabilities%5D.%20The%20environment%20at%20Hydra%20is%20caring%20and%20non-threatening.%20This%20encourages%20the%20children%20to%20let%20go%20of%20any%20stress%20and%20feelings%20of%20low%20self-worth%20that%20often%20accompany%20the%20condition%20of%20dyslexia.%20It%20helps%20them%20feel%20accepted%20for%20who%20they%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVNHQZmfjK0s%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMDA%20also%20engages%20in%20Occupational%20Therapy%2C%20a%20key%20component%20of%20remediation.%20This%20focuses%20%E2%80%9Con%20helping%20children%20with%20physical%20ability%2C%20sensory%20integration%2C%20attention%2C%20and%20concentration%20difficulty%20to%20enhance%20their%20skills%20along%20with%20self-esteem%20and%20performance%20in%20the%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20you%20have%20counselling%2C%20where%20the%20ALRC%20partners%20with%20qualified%20professionals%20to%20provide%20counselling%20for%20children%20and%20parents%20as%20part%20of%20the%20personality%20development%20of%20the%20child.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20in-house%20counsellor%20who%20interacts%20with%20the%20child%20and%20the%20parent%20and%20also%20conducts%20periodic%20workshops%20for%20them.%20The%20teachers%20are%20also%20given%20orientation%20on%20child%20behaviour%20to%20help%20them%20handle%20different%20behavioural%20issues%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20website%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EResults%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20misconceptions%20that%20people%20have%20about%20dyslexic%20children%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20intelligent.%20Actually%2C%20they%20are%20very%20intelligent%20with%20an%20IQ%20of%20more%20than%2085.%20It%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20work%20with%20them%20once%20we%20take%20the%20right%20approach.%20MDA%20has%20removed%20the%20misconceptions%20by%20demonstrating%20the%20remedial%20programmes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20three%20decades%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20claims%20that%20MDA%20has%20directly%20assisted%20more%20than%201%2C500%20children%20in%20their%20full-time%20remediation%20centre%2C%20and%20provided%20part-time%20remediation%20for%203%2C000%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20trained%20more%20than%202%2C000%20teachers%20and%20conducted%20training%20programmes%20in%20over%20400%20schools.%20We%20have%20also%20set%20up%20resource%20rooms%20for%20dyslexic%20children%20in%20nearly%20200%20schools%20that%20benefit%2010%2C000%20of%20them%20year%20on%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Chandrasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20far%20has%20our%20education%20system%20come%20in%20assisting%20children%20with%20dyslexia%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20education%20system%20has%20shown%20a%20lot%20of%20understanding%20towards%20the%20needs%20of%20dyslexic%20children.%20A%20lot%20of%20concessions%20are%20offered%20during%20public%20exams.%20Dyslexic%20children%20are%20eligible%20for%20all%20the%20benefits%20under%20the%20Disabilities%20Act.%20Yet%2C%20we%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20Awareness%20in%20schools%20is%20still%20very%20low%2C%20especially%20among%20teachers.%20While%20private%20schools%20easily%20understand%20the%20problems%20associated%20with%20dyslexia%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20not%20a%20priority%20in%20government%20schools.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20D%20Chandrasekhar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730518200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMDA-Image-2-1730298658.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D373627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%201992%2C%20a%20compassionate%20group%20of%20parents%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20philanthropists%20came%20together%20to%20create%20the%20Madras%20Dyslexia%20Association%20(MDA).%20Their%20mission%20is%20to%20support%20children%20with%20dyslexia%20through%20pragmatic%20solutions%2C%20focusing%20on%20personalized%20education%20and%20creating%20an%20understanding%20environment%20that%20empowers%20these%20children%20to%20thrive%20academically%20and%20socially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373627%2Fhelping-dyslexic-children-with-learning-education-madras-dyslexia-association-iit-madras%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20soldier%20raised%20his%20weapon%20at%20me'%3A%20Teenager%20forcibly%20separated%20from%20family%20as%20Israel%20evacuates%2090%25%20of%20North%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730478060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F11%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-gaza-idf_6737176.jpg%3F20241102222516%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fteenager-describes-forced-separation-from-family-as-israel-evacuates-90-of-north-gaza-13246122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%