ct%20potable%20water%20reuse%20project%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20project%20uses%20an%20environmental%20buffer%20like%20a%20lake%20for%20dilution%20with%20rainwater%20and%2For%20a%20groundwater%20aquifer%20for%20earth%20filtration.%20This%20water%20eventually%20goes%20through%20a%20final%20treatment%20stage%20before%20it%20is%20supplied%20to%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20project%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20effort%20to%20rejuvenate%2065%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20employing%20treated%20wastewater%20and%20rainwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20project%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20involves%20reviving%20an%20old%20well%20and%20digging%20borewells%20to%20access%20the%20aquifer%2C%20along%20with%20the%20installation%20of%20water%20treatment%20plants%20in%20two%20phases.%20Now%2C%20the%20system%20provides%206.4%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20daily%2C%20helping%20supplement%20the%20domestic%20water%20requirement%20of%2045%2C000%20residents%20in%20Devanahalli.%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20collaboration%20of%20many%20organisations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Carl%20Zeiss%2C%20Rotary%20South%20Parade%20Bangalore%2C%20and%20Wipro%20Foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20water%20crisis%20and%20lake%20rejuvenation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com