er%2C%20and%20explore%20how%20a%20town%20can%20become%20self-sufficient%20by%20using%20both%20local%20water%20sources%20and%20treated%20wastewater.%20The%20project%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20meet%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%205.4%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20per%20day)%20water%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5B1%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20per%20day)%20is%20equal%20to%201%2C000%20KLD%20(thousand%20litres%20per%20day)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0019-1730297076.jpg%3Ffit%3D1600%252C719%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20water%20shortage%20can%20be%20addressed%20by%20wastewater%20treatment%20and%20lake%20rejuvenation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0019-1730297076.jpg%3Fw%3D1600%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0019-1730297076.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C135%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0019-1730297076.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C225%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0019-1730297076.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C345%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2